The Vig is awesome. Perfect place to go with friends or coworkers after a long day at the office to have a glass of wine off and enjoy either an appetizer or my favorite Steak Salad. Also a great place for people watching since you get an eclectic mix of the Scottsdale/Phoenix scene.

